{"tid":501921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔止叫雞用得 支付寶進駐港鐵　親！","createTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T11:18:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b929029ca8f98fb67d1e2ae80024502a98a53d44","tid":501921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s7.postimg.org/ezsh5gstn/1217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs7.postimg.org%2Fezsh5gstn%2F1217.jpg&h=50f9c29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前消息指，支付寶母公司螞蟻金服擬於港鐵推動透過支付寶買車票。16日支付寶於官方微博正式宣佈，港鐵乘客及遊客均可以在羅湖站及落馬洲站，用支付寶或支付寶HK購買車票。另外除支付寶外，售票機亦容許乘客以微信支付購買車票。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶表示由即日開始，乘客可使用支付寶於港鐵站購買單程票，但只限於羅湖及落馬洲兩個過境口岸站，為乘客及內地遊客提供更多的付款選擇。於落馬洲站，目前只有一部售票機可用支付寶付款，不少來港旅客向職員詢問用法。支付寶購買單程車票以港元為單位，價格亦與用現金購買單程車票一樣。"},{"pid":"9fc35d72840b6914d6529a4fa76dcc713125a31d","tid":501921,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"巴打岩岩放監？"},{"pid":"c939a59087d321f76cd23748829e57fbaf868c00","tid":501921,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛D wade: 八達通引入QR code, 所以QR code安全</span>"},{"pid":"690c085e84c130e7d1f14b18b721e7cd0cc5990a","tid":501921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打岩岩放監？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問毒果：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171217/20247427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F20247427&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2ea94213\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F20247427&h=61952bbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171217/20247427</a>"},{"pid":"1c1e022280f